---
title: Pan-Seared Steak with Pan Sauce and Warm Potato Salad
description: Our tasty pan sauce pulls no punches, and this dish really lets it shine. For balance, we've paired it with our creamy potato salad,  featuring crunchy green beans and hint of dill.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/steak-poele-99458696.jpg
